1.value: This is a web application built with the GrapeCity Spread.Sheets JavaScript Spreadsheet component. It mimics much of the functionality and UI you see in with Microsoft Windows Store Excel application. This application was built to showcase the features and extensibility you will find in Spread.Sheets
- Each tab contains samples of features that can be implemented with Spread.Sheets.
- You can create a new workbook by choosing "New" from the file menu.
- This application will save and load .SSJSON files which are readable by Spread.Sheets
